                        <interp inst="t18410510-name-463" type="given" value="FREDERICK JOHN"></interp>FREDERICK JOHN BROWN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am clerk to a ship-broker, and live in Bartholomew-close. I knew the prisoner by sight, in Mr. Watson's ser-vice—I was at the London-bridge wharf on business, and saw him on board a Gravesend steamer—I gave information—he was taken into cus<lb></lb>tody.</p>
