                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> Mrs. Watson delivered the plate to the prisoner to clean—she is not here—I only know he applied to her for it, from her telling me—there is nobody here who saw it in his possession after he left the premises—there is no witness who knows the prisoner had the plate at all.</p>
